Allstate Assurance Company Separate Account B Key Developments

Allstate Assurance Company Separate Account B, Annual General Meeting, Jun 15, 2016
May 4 16
Allstate Assurance Company Separate Account B, Annual General Meeting, Jun 15, 2016, at 15:00 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: Unum Group Building Conference Room 7E, 1 Fountain Square Chattanooga, TN 37402 Tennessee United States Agenda: To consider election of 3 members of the board of managers in accordance with the rules and regulations of the separate account; to ratify the selection and appointment of Deloitte & Touche LLP as the independent auditors for the separate account in accordance with the rules and regulations of the separate account; and to transact such other business as may properly come before the meeting and any adjournment thereof.


